<body>
    <h1>LLM Memory Tools</h1>
    <p>Download the Go client binaries for your platform. All binaries read
    <code>.agent.json</code> for auth credentials.</p>

    <h2>memory-sync</h2>
    <p>Bidirectional sync of local memory files and conversation logs with the remote notes store.</p>
    <table>
        <tr><th>Platform</th><th>Architecture</th><th>Download</th></tr>
        <tr><td>Linux</td><td>x86_64</td><td><a href="memory-sync_linux_amd64">memory-sync_linux_amd64</a></td></tr>
        <tr><td>Linux</td><td>ARM64</td><td><a href="memory-sync_linux_arm64">memory-sync_linux_arm64</a></td></tr>
        <tr><td>macOS</td><td>Intel</td><td><a href="memory-sync_darwin_amd64">memory-sync_darwin_amd64</a></td></tr>
        <tr><td>macOS</td><td>Apple Silicon</td><td><a href="memory-sync_darwin_arm64">memory-sync_darwin_arm64</a></td></tr>
        <tr><td>Windows</td><td>x86_64</td><td><a href="memory-sync_windows_amd64.exe">memory-sync_windows_amd64.exe</a></td></tr>
        <tr><td>Windows</td><td>ARM64</td><td><a href="memory-sync_windows_arm64.exe">memory-sync_windows_arm64.exe</a></td></tr>
    </table>

    <h2>mail-send</h2>
    <p>Send mail to another agent with the body read from a local file. Use this for large bodies (diffs, review reports) so the content never has to be passed as a string argument.</p>
    <table>
        <tr><th>Platform</th><th>Architecture</th><th>Download</th></tr>
        <tr><td>Linux</td><td>x86_64</td><td><a href="mail-send_linux_amd64">mail-send_linux_amd64</a></td></tr>
        <tr><td>Linux</td><td>ARM64</td><td><a href="mail-send_linux_arm64">mail-send_linux_arm64</a></td></tr>
        <tr><td>macOS</td><td>Intel</td><td><a href="mail-send_darwin_amd64">mail-send_darwin_amd64</a></td></tr>
        <tr><td>macOS</td><td>Apple Silicon</td><td><a href="mail-send_darwin_arm64">mail-send_darwin_arm64</a></td></tr>
        <tr><td>Windows</td><td>x86_64</td><td><a href="mail-send_windows_amd64.exe">mail-send_windows_amd64.exe</a></td></tr>
        <tr><td>Windows</td><td>ARM64</td><td><a href="mail-send_windows_arm64.exe">mail-send_windows_arm64.exe</a></td></tr>
    </table>

    <p class="note">These binaries are updated automatically from
    <a href="https://github.com/jeffdafoe/llm-memory-api/releases">GitHub Releases</a>.</p>
